# 🚀 QuickAI – AI Powered SaaS Platform

QuickAI is a full-stack AI-powered SaaS application where users can generate AI content like images, articles, blogs, summaries, background removal, and more using multiple AI APIs.

Users can also publish their creations to a community page where others can like and explore AI-generated content.

---

# 🌐 Live Demo

## 🔗 Backend Live
https://saas-app-4oq8.vercel.app/

## 🔗 Frontend Project Live
https://saas-app-aim7.vercel.app/

---

# ✨ Features

- 🔐 Authentication using Clerk
- 🧠 AI Text Generation
- 🎨 AI Image Generation
- 🖼️ Background Removal
- 📄 PDF/Text Summarization
- ❤️ Community Likes System
- 🌍 Public Community Feed
- ☁️ Cloudinary Image Upload
- 🗄️ Neon PostgreSQL Database
- ⚡ Fast & Responsive UI
- 📱 Fully Responsive Design

---

# 🛠️ Tech Stack

## Frontend
- React.js
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios
- Clerk Authentication
- React Toastify
- Lucide React Icons

## Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL (Neon DB)
- Cloudinary
- Clerk Backend Auth
- Multer
- OpenAI API
- ClipDrop API

## Deployment
- Vercel
- Neon Database
- Cloudinary

